            <title>
                <![CDATA[ 亚洲海工四巨头在想什么？干什么？——价值深耕与中国船厂启示录 ]]>
            </title>
            <link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3hoDWjBbfhhhxxDKSVeHrw</link>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[ fff 在全球能源转型与海洋工程装备市场复苏的双重背景下，新加坡海庭（Seatrium）、韩国三星重工、HD现代重工与韩华海洋这四家亚洲顶级海工船厂近期相继发布2025年业绩及战略规划。通过对四家企业的深度分析，可以清晰看到亚洲海工业正在经历一场深刻的战略转向：从过去的规模扩张... ]]>
            </description>
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[ fff <div class="rich_media_content" id="js_content"><p data-pm-slice="0 0 []"><b><span leaf=""><img alt="Seatrium continues its divestment series - Offshore Energy" class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.4808795411089866" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1046" height="335" width="697" data-imgfileid="100002821" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_jpg/ayJA4003Iib7eHslicSZOxKtayo85bzZUibfiaCV2icHicv53c9dk9tVG7ibjf6D1gAKJUFY36C8t6rL8ySjfQUGicP6Pbia4NiakEIcHJTuEU0OVZ0Fs/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></b><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">在全球能源转型与海洋工程装备市场复苏的双重背景下，新加坡海庭（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Seatrium</span></span><span leaf="">）、韩国三星重工、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工与韩华海洋这四家亚洲顶级海工船厂近期相继发布</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年业绩及战略规划。通过对四家企业的深度分析，可以清晰看到亚洲海工业正在经历一场深刻的战略转向：从过去的规模扩张转向价值深耕，从单纯的装备制造向全生命周期解决方案供应商转型。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span leaf="">一、战略调整：殊途同归的价值取向</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span leaf="">四家企业在战略层面呈现出高度一致的转型方向，但在实施路径上各具特色。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">海庭正在加速推进</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">瘦身强体</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">战略。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年初以来，公司密集处置非核心资产：以</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1.04</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元出售新加坡</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">17</span></span><span leaf="">艘拖船船队，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1690</span></span><span leaf="">万新元处置</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"Can-Do 2"</span></span><span leaf="">浮船坞，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2200</span></span><span leaf="">万新元出售印尼卡里汶岛船厂，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1250</span></span><span leaf="">万新元转让新加坡</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Crescent Yard</span></span><span leaf="">，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">6500</span></span><span leaf="">万新元完成美国</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">AmFELS</span></span><span leaf="">船厂出售。这一系列资产剥离预计将为公司带来超过</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">5000</span></span><span leaf="">万新元的年度运营成本节约，使其能够更专注于</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">等核心海工装备建造与集成业务。海庭的战略意图十分清晰：通过资产轻量化，将资源集中于高附加值领域。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">三星重工则选择了</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">聚焦</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG+</span></span><span leaf="">全球合作</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">的发展路径。公司目前同时在巨济造船厂推进马来西亚国家石油公司</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">ZLNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目、加拿大</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Cedar LNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目及莫桑比克</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Coral North</span></span><span leaf="">项目等</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3</span></span><span leaf="">个</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">建造工程，并即将与美国</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Delfin Midstream</span></span><span leaf="">公司签订新的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">订单。与此同时，三星重工积极拓展全球合作网络，近期与卡塔尔国有船厂</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">QSTS</span></span><span leaf="">签署谅解备忘录，共同拓展中东环保船舶改造市场；通过与越南船厂合作建造原油运输船，优化全球产能布局。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-no-proof:yes;"><span leaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.5616045845272206" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1047" height="392" width="698" data-imgfileid="100002818" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/ayJA4003Iib4jSxgmiaZnZUnfY0RMHnDVs2LPXBcWQqxfA4ISkGTKczAw1gWDw2WIC9ElXTtVguujHmSdxq7euiaqvRavUZHH69uX6IufSbmz8/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工走的是一条</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">内部整合</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">+</span></span><span leaf="">特种船突破</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">的道路。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12</span></span><span leaf="">月</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1</span></span><span leaf="">日，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工与</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代尾浦正式完成合并，新成立的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工旨在集结子公司力量放大协同效应。在业务布局上，公司将</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年特种船订单目标设定为</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">30</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，是</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实际业绩的约</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3</span></span><span leaf="">倍，全力开拓军舰、巡逻舰、潜艇等特种船舶市场。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-no-proof:yes;"><span leaf=""><img alt="Shipbuilding market shakeup: South Korea's HD Hyundai Heavy Industries and HD Hyundai Mipo to merge - Offshore Energy" class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.7994269340974212" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1047" height="558" width="698" data-imgfileid="100002820" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/ayJA4003Iib5k3qomG2B3Coh1ckmh9GN1sOu5YJIAEYicqQHwb0NVeWZzwsltniaEoxYiazYibFfQ2mClamRI7RQhO237qmE232jMNOfgsooW6Xw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">韩华海洋的战略转型最为彻底。自</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2023</span></span><span leaf="">年并入韩华集团后，公司明确提出从传统</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPC</span></span><span leaf="">承包商向</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">及海上风电等领域的一揽子承包方式（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCIO</span></span><span leaf="">）解决方案供应商升级的战略目标。为支撑这一转型，公司在荷兰阿姆斯特丹设立全球项目中心（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">GPC</span></span><span leaf="">），聘请原</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">SBM Offshore</span></span><span leaf="">美洲区总裁</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Philippe Levy</span></span><span leaf="">担任海洋事业部部长，并在印度诺伊达设立全球工程交付中心，构建起</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">国内总装</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">+</span></span><span leaf="">海外模块协同</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">的多码头生产体系。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-no-proof:yes;"><span leaf=""><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.3191287878787879" data-type="png" data-w="1056" height="225" width="704" data-imgfileid="100002819" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_jpg/ayJA4003Iib7TTZzEjAgLvRX8m8I3zX3SwyDSqNlIXxIh86syPLrovdtFDOcVFnumic3PgLXxP9MYR7u9L85ib9B1UA3qUqPkaurzXf2IbIDRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span leaf="">二、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">业务：订单与布局的全面较量</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">作为海洋工程装备皇冠上的明珠，是四家企业战略布局的重中之重。从在手订单和项目储备来看，各家企业呈现出不同的竞争态势。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">海庭：</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">FPSO</span></span></span><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">领域绝对领先</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">在手订单方面，海庭实力最为雄厚。公司</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年向巴西国家石油公司成功交付</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-78 FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">，这是其为巴国油建造的六艘新一代环保</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">的首艘，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-78</span></span><span leaf="">于</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12</span></span><span leaf="">月</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">31</span></span><span leaf="">日实现首油，彰显了海庭从工程、建造到海上调试的全链条能力。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2024</span></span><span leaf="">年，海庭获得巴西国家石油公司</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Atapu</span></span><span leaf="">和</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Sepia</span></span><span leaf="">油田项目的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-84</span></span><span leaf="">和</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-85 FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">合同，总金额高达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">81.6</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元。值得注意的是，海庭是该项目的唯一投标方，反映出其在</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">领域的独特竞争优势。截至</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年底，海庭净订单簿达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">178</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元（交付至</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2033</span></span><span leaf="">年），涵盖</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">24</span></span><span leaf="">个项目。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">同时，海庭未来</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">24</span></span><span leaf="">个月投标管道总价值高达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">320</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元（约</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">253.3</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元），其中油气项目约占</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">230</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元，过半瞄准南美市场。公司已向巴西国家石油公司表达参与</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">BOT</span></span><span leaf="">模式</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">项目竞标的意向，包括</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-86</span></span><span leaf="">等项目，并确认将采取与运营伙伴合作的策略竞标</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">BOT</span></span><span leaf="">项目。在市场布局上，海庭采取巴西与圭亚那双线突破的策略：在巴西，公司拥有三家成熟船厂，具备本土化含量优势；在圭亚那，通过参与埃克森美孚</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Stabroek</span></span><span leaf="">区块所有</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">项目，在高价值集成和上部模块建造领域占据有利地位。</span></p><p data-pm-slice="2 3 []"><span leaf=""><br></span></p><section style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NjM0NzY2MA==&amp;mid=2247486435&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=17d7477918388eddad971f2705116f8e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" imgurl="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/MQwxJuNh6g55fZYV7CibqMB1ZiclPJh9ia9cp5dDIhUjq6CA3sZhggLic9uBCB9SBGyJbgEGh6PUt433SPwXOtn01g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" linktype="image" tab="innerlink" data-itemshowtype="0" target="_blank" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.68515625" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" type="block" data-imgfileid="100002782" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/MQwxJuNh6g55fZYV7CibqMB1ZiclPJh9ia9cp5dDIhUjq6CA3sZhggLic9uBCB9SBGyJbgEGh6PUt433SPwXOtn01g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></a></section><section style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NjM0NzY2MA==&amp;mid=2247486435&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b0bfb0048b745cc6efcb4f510a3083c4&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" imgurl="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/MQwxJuNh6g55fZYV7CibqMB1ZiclPJh9ia9OFzdtdJvwulMISNIYgQsGhAatebQRoaicasv8smcDcdGJdibDEuwKiaDQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" linktype="image" tab="innerlink" data-itemshowtype="0" target="_blank" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.68515625" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" type="block" data-imgfileid="100002775" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/mmecoa_jpg/MQwxJuNh6g55fZYV7CibqMB1ZiclPJh9ia9OFzdtdJvwulMISNIYgQsGhAatebQRoaicasv8smcDcdGJdibDEuwKiaDQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></a></section><section style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NjM0NzY2MA==&amp;mid=2247486446&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=49c765e1036184d2f28b33066918aec8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" imgurl="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/ayJA4003Iib6VDGB0eMLNx65cZjh3M9fb5ZheD8Z9CW0icaDcxlzrOFC9yGGibfwgKR11HEPhFEoU02Nwmw8hX6KyWElf2dGaZcZjYdpMszxic4/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" linktype="image" tab="innerlink" data-itemshowtype="0" target="_blank" data-linktype="1"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.6827956989247311" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1302" type="block" data-imgfileid="100002794" data-aistatus="1" src="https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/ayJA4003Iib6VDGB0eMLNx65cZjh3M9fb5ZheD8Z9CW0icaDcxlzrOFC9yGGibfwgKR11HEPhFEoU02Nwmw8hX6KyWElf2dGaZcZjYdpMszxic4/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" style="max-width: 600px"></span></a></section><p><span leaf=""><br></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">韩华海洋：强势回归</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">FPSO</span></span></span><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">领域</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">韩华海洋</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">11</span></span><span leaf="">月为巴西国家石油公司建造的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-79 FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">顺利交付启航，预计将于</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2</span></span><span leaf="">月抵达巴西</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Bezios</span></span><span leaf="">深海油田。该</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">设计日产原油</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">18</span></span><span leaf="">万桶、天然气</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">720</span></span><span leaf="">万立方米，最大储油量达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">200</span></span><span leaf="">万桶，是全球最大规模深海油田的关键生产单元，总价值约</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">23</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元（与意大利</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Saipem</span></span><span leaf="">联合中标）。尽管建造过程中发生意外事故，但最终仍按合同期限完成交付。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">此外，韩华海洋正全力竞标巴西国油的新一代</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">项目</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-86</span></span><span leaf="">，这是公司自</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2023</span></span><span leaf="">年更名后首次挑战</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">新项目，也是时隔四年重返全球海工装备市场的关键一役。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-86</span></span><span leaf="">采用</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">BOT</span></span><span leaf="">模式，对投标企业的财务与运营能力提出更高要求。此外，公司还将目光投向巴西国油的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-91</span></span><span leaf="">项目、道达尔能源的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Venus</span></span><span leaf="">项目，并已入围利比亚</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Zone E</span></span><span leaf="">油气田开发项目</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCI</span></span><span leaf="">承包商最终候选名单，该海上平台项目价值</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">30-40</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元。战略布局上，韩华海洋将</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年海洋工程部门订单目标设定为</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">32.6</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，相比</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年仅获得</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1</span></span><span leaf="">艘海洋工程订单的惨淡业绩，目标大幅提升。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">三星重工：聚焦</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">FLNG</span></span></span><span leaf=""><span textstyle="" style="font-weight: bold;">差异化竞争</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">三星重工截至</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1</span></span><span leaf="">月底累计手持订单</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">134</span></span><span leaf="">艘、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">287</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元。在浮式生产装备领域，公司选择</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">作为差异化竞争方向，目前正在巨济造船厂同时推进马来西亚国家石油公司</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">ZLNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目、加拿大</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Cedar LNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目及莫桑比克</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Coral North</span></span><span leaf="">项目等</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3</span></span><span leaf="">个</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">建造工程，并即将与美国</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Delfin Midstream</span></span><span leaf="">公司签订新的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">订单。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">目前，三星重工已入围利比亚</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Zone E</span></span><span leaf="">油气田开发项目</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCI</span></span><span leaf="">承包商最终候选名单，同时</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Delfin FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目和</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Coral FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目也在谈判范围内。公司设定了</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年接单目标</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">139</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，较</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实际接单激增</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">76%</span></span><span leaf="">，并正在推进</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">5</span></span><span leaf="">个以上</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">项目的谈判。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工：特种船与海工并举</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年海洋工程部门实际订单仅</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1.33</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，远低于年初设定的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">18.84</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元目标，在</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">领域布局相对有限。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">公司同样也入围了利比亚</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">Zone E</span></span><span leaf="">油气田开发项目</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCI</span></span><span leaf="">承包商最终候选名单，同时全力争取加拿大巡逻潜艇项目（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">CPSP</span></span><span leaf="">）。业绩目标上，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工将</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年海洋工程部门订单目标设定为</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">32.59</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，远超</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实际业绩，显示出强烈的追赶意图。公司还计划通过海上变电站项目切入海洋能源领域，将</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年打造为正式进军新能源业务的元年。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span leaf="">三、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年业绩：复苏态势全面确认</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年四家企业的业绩表现全面确认了海工市场的复苏态势。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">海庭实现全年收入</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">115</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">24%</span></span><span leaf="">；净利润达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3.236</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元，较</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2024</span></span><span leaf="">年实现</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">106%</span></span><span leaf="">的翻倍增长，较</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2023</span></span><span leaf="">年亏损超</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">20</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元的困境显著逆转。毛利率从</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3.1%</span></span><span leaf="">改善至</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">7.4%</span></span><span leaf="">，主要得益于巴西国家石油公司</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P</span></span><span leaf="">系列</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">等项目的顺利推进。公司未来</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">24</span></span><span leaf="">个月的净投标管道价值高达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">320</span></span><span leaf="">亿新元。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">三星重工</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实现营业收入</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">106.5</span></span><span leaf="">万亿韩元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">7.5%</span></span><span leaf="">；实现营业利润</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">8622</span></span><span leaf="">亿韩元，同比暴增</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">71.5%</span></span><span leaf="">，创下</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12</span></span><span leaf="">年来的最高纪录，营业利润率达到</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">8%</span></span><span leaf="">。这是公司自</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2023</span></span><span leaf="">年扭亏以来连续第三年实现盈利。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">韩国造船海洋</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实现营业收入</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">71.26</span></span><span leaf="">万亿韩元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">5.2%</span></span><span leaf="">；实现营业利润</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">6.10</span></span><span leaf="">万亿韩元，同比暴增</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">104.5%</span></span><span leaf="">。其中，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工自身销售额达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12</span></span><span leaf="">万亿美元，营业利润</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1.39</span></span><span leaf="">万亿美元，同比分别增长</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">21.4%</span></span><span leaf="">和</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">188.9%</span></span><span leaf="">。公司全年累计接单达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">133</span></span><span leaf="">艘、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">181.6</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，连续五年达成接单目标。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">韩华海洋</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年实现营业收入</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12.69</span></span><span leaf="">万亿韩元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">18%</span></span><span leaf="">；实现营业利润</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">1.11</span></span><span leaf="">万亿韩元，同比暴增</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">366%</span></span><span leaf="">，成功扭亏为盈并突破万亿韩元利润大关。截至</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年底，公司全年累计承接新船订单</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">43</span></span><span leaf="">艘、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">100.5</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，其中</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">VLCC</span></span><span leaf="">接单量位居全球首位。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span leaf="">四、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">市场总体情况与竞争格局</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span leaf="">全球</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">市场正迎来新一轮复苏周期。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2024</span></span><span leaf="">年第二季度以来，</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">订单累计订单额达</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">120</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元，共</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3</span></span><span leaf="">艘。能源海事协会（</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EMA</span></span><span leaf="">）识别出未来</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">12</span></span><span leaf="">个月内最可能授予的</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">29</span></span><span leaf="">个浮式生产项目，包括</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">16</span></span><span leaf="">艘</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">7</span></span><span leaf="">艘</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FSO</span></span><span leaf="">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">3</span></span><span leaf="">艘</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FLNG</span></span><span leaf="">等。巴西、圭亚那、纳米比亚、安哥拉、印度尼西亚等地区需求旺盛。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">竞争格局正在发生深刻变化。海庭凭借</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-84/P-85</span></span><span leaf="">项目成为市场领导者，作为唯一投标方中标</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">81.6</span></span><span leaf="">亿美元大单，反映出</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">市场产能有限、头部企业优势明显的特征。韩国三家船厂</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2025</span></span><span leaf="">年在商船领域表现强劲，但海洋工程领域除韩华海洋</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">P-79</span></span><span leaf="">交付外，整体订单不及预期。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">2026</span></span><span leaf="">年韩国船厂普遍将海工装备作为重点突破方向，目标大幅提升。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><b><span leaf="">五、中国船厂的借鉴与启示</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></b></p><p><span leaf="">四家亚洲顶级海工船厂的战略动向为中国船厂提供了多方面的借鉴。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">第一，专业化聚焦是提升竞争力的必由之路。海庭通过大规模资产剥离，将资源集中于</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">等核心海工业务；韩华海洋明确聚焦</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">战略，全力向</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCIO</span></span><span leaf="">解决方案供应商转型。中国船厂应审视自身业务组合，果断剥离非核心、低效资产，将有限资源集中于具有比较优势的细分领域，避免</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">大而全</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">的规模扩张陷阱。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">第二，商业模式创新是获取更高价值的关键。海庭积极竞标</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">BOT</span></span><span leaf="">模式</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">项目，韩华海洋向</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">EPCIO</span></span><span leaf="">解决方案供应商转型，都体现了从单纯装备制造向</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">制造</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">+</span></span><span leaf="">服务</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">商业模式升级的趋势。中国船厂应积极探索工程总包、融资租赁、运营维护等多元化商业模式，向产业链高端延伸，获取更高价值份额。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">第三，全球化布局是突破市场壁垒的有效手段。海庭在巴西拥有三家成熟船厂，通过本土化满足当地含量要求；韩华海洋在荷兰设立全球项目中心，在印度设立工程交付中心，构建全球化产能与工程协同体系。中国船厂应借鉴这一思路，通过海外设厂、技术合作、人才引进等方式，突破区域市场壁垒，提升全球资源配置能力。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">第四，人才国际化是提升技术能力的重要途径。韩华海洋聘请原</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">SBM Offshore</span></span><span leaf="">美洲区总裁担任海洋事业部部长，引进具备国际顶尖海工经验的管理团队，快速提升</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">FPSO</span></span><span leaf="">项目能力。中国船厂应加大国际化人才引进力度，通过</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">引进来</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">与</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">走出去</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">"</span></span><span leaf="">相结合，快速提升在高端海工领域的技术与管理能力。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">第五，数字化转型是构筑未来竞争优势的必然选择。</span><span lang="EN-US"><span leaf="">HD</span></span><span leaf="">现代重工正加快基于人工智能与机器人技术的数字化转型，力争在零碳船舶市场掌握主导权。中国船厂应加大智能制造、数字孪生、绿色技术等领域的投入，通过数字化转型提升生产效率、降低成本、增强环保性能，构筑面向未来的竞争优势。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><p><span leaf="">亚洲海工四巨头的战略新动向揭示了一个清晰的趋势：海工装备市场正在从周期性复苏转向结构性变革。那些能够聚焦核心能力、创新商业模式、布局全球资源、引进国际人才、加速数字化转型的企业，将在这场变革中赢得先机。对于中国船厂而言，借鉴这些领先企业的战略思路，结合自身优势找准定位，方能在新一轮海工竞争中获得更大发展空间。</span><span lang="EN-US"><p></p></span></p><section nodeleaf=""><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-nickname="SinorigOffshore" data-from="2" data-headimg="http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MQwxJuNh6g5F5rVjiaeePv5MxmWnGlq01XyJywrDv4e0VmvQuDhjOmWZxSayHxHia3JzRhtKIzBciapW6FgicuEmxA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-signature="SinorigOffshore是中国海洋工程信息与咨询专家。" data-id="MzU1NjM0NzY2MA==" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><section><span leaf=""><br></span></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div><br><div> 平台地址：<a href="http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/DhmBRYqDVI">http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/DhmBRYqDVI</a></div><img alt="" width="1px" height="1px" class="" style="width:1px;height:1px;display:none" src="http://www.jintiankansha.me/rss_static/133666/DhmBRYqDVI"> ]]>
